summary:
I am a passionate Content Marketing Strategist with a specialisation in Performance Marketing, Social Media Marketing and Influencer Marketing that enjoys working in fast-paced, international environments.

I am always on top of the latest social media trends and am passionate about creating tailor-made digital communication frameworks for brands. 

In my current role as Content Marketing Strategist I focus on delivering content marketing and social media marketing strategies to various international clients, in order for them to not only reach their desired target audience, but also to inspire and convert them.
